{"tid":983084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★支那化？消委會：35款餅卷含污染物　泰昌無印良品下架","createTime":"2019-01-15T16:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T10:39:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"680e900904bc87b8194b17be0a626ea3d0839aa3","tid":983084,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VatAhp0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVatAhp0.jpg&h=dec69fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iBFu6im.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiBFu6im.jpg&h=240c7c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n農曆新年拜年時每家必備曲奇，但多食卻未必「身體健康」。消委會驗出市面58款餅卷類食品，包括蛋卷、蝴蝶酥、曲奇、杏仁條等，發現35款樣本含污染物氯丙二醇(3-MCPD)，長期攝入可損害腎臟功能及影響雄性(男性)生殖系統，亦有多款曲奇含基因致癌物。<br />\n<br />\n測試中氯丙二醇(3-MCPD)含量最高的樣本為「泰昌餅家」蝴蝶酥，每公斤有780微克，其次為每公斤含669微克的「LU Palmito L'Original Sweet Dry Biscuit」。香港現時對此未有規管，根據歐洲食品安全局建議，人體每公斤體重可攝入2微克，即一名60公斤成年人，每日攝取量不應多於120微克，以「泰昌餅家」蝴蝶酥為例，進食154克，即20塊就會超出建議標準。<br />\n<br />\n測試中有40款曲奇含基因致癌物環氧丙醇，最高含量者為「元朗榮華」，每公斤含1900微克；在非預先包裝或獲豁免營養標籤的預先包裝樣本中，環氧丙醇含量最高的是無印良品的Oats Crunch Sable Hazehut，每公斤1100微克。另外亦有42款含基因致癌物丙烯酰胺，最高含量者為「Sainsbury's」，每公斤含340微克。由於兩者為基因致癌物，世衞不能為其釐定安全攝取量，建議盡量少攝取。<br />\n<br />\n泰昌餅家回應指，現時出售的產品包括蝴蝶酥均符合現行法例要求，但明白事件有機會引起消費者疑慮，決定即日起主動暫時停售該產品，亦會進一步與供應商及有關政府機構了解，期望可改良食材成分，以為消費者尋求最佳的保障。<br />\n<br />\n無印良品發言人亦稱，今日(15日)已停售Oats Crunch Sable Hazelnut，已購買的顧客可退貨或換貨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190115/bkn-20190115100029883-0115_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190115%2Fbkn-20190115100029883-0115_00822_001.html&d=3FxtQXKnySIOnRdxwobdHAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=049aa4f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190115/bkn-20190115100029883-0115_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"46c66879fc42f668bf48c324b1a1b600d5db2884","tid":983084,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190115/photo/bkn-20190115100029883-0115_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190115232726\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190115100029883-0115_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190115232726&h=fcc171b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bab0073d7ae9893fa0003181644c2334458d75e0","tid":983084,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6e5109f59f951c45c27dd1606d9e4c455cdc7d","tid":983084,"uid":57700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ccbabc612254f0c5e2e79e7471095953b61c7be","tid":983084,"uid":62950,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/223431_1b9849617ef9c66f0f5163bf8d7d0616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F223431_1b9849617ef9c66f0f5163bf8d7d0616.jpg&h=f1337d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘉頓什餅又嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a48df3c45a96b173af76792b063d16ddec8a12","tid":983084,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce6e5109f59f951c45c27dd1606d9e4c455cdc7d","tid":983084,"uid":57700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"又嬴"},{"pid":"869052041f48a2bb549c33d8c1dcc66be7eba5d0","tid":983084,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T16:51:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97fe1994a33bb1efdf9c8f0db9c9901b9670991e"